Still in the design stages, the first central London luxury hotel nursery of its kind, Grosvenor House's baby bedroom will be called Suite Dreams, and aims 'to provide parents with a quintessentially British, unique home-from-home experience'.

The room, fit for a future king or queen, will be fitted with 1920s-style furnishings in keeping with the hotel's traditional bedroom suites for adults. 

