There will be three bespoke (and aptly named) packages available for the nursery: Buckingham, Windsor and Clarence.

The grand Buckingham package - a three-night stay starting from £6,270 - includes a range of luxurious pampering activities, from a complimentary cut and blow dry at Sanrizz for mum, a men's shave at Alfred Dunhill for, as well as a private consultation with the Dragons of Walton Street.

